---
title: TLS / mTLS termination (quiver-crypto / server)
---
sequenceDiagram
  participant CL as Client
  participant SV as quiver-server (rustls)
  CL->>SV: ClientHello
  SV-->>CL: ServerHello + cert chain
  CL->>CL: validate chain (ring provider)
  opt mTLS
    SV->>CL: CertificateRequest
    CL-->>SV: client cert
    SV->>SV: validate client cert
  end
  CL->>SV: Finished (session keys)
  Note over CL,SV: encrypted gRPC / REST
